{"data":[{"date":"09:56 11/08","title":"Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn ra th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/unai-emery-da-chon-ra-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City, v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh m\u1eafc 6 l\u1ed7i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 48 b\u00e0n thua \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/unai-emery-da-chon-ra-thu-mon-bat-chinh-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Cech s\u1ebd b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City thay v\u00ec Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-bernd-leno-chinh-thuc-chon-so-ao-o-arsenal-172-190840.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua Leno</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do Petr Cech \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i. HLV Emery \u0111ang \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo The Telegraph, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Unai Emery s\u1ebd b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Petr Cech b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City, v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Cech thay v\u00ec t\u00e2n binh Leno. C\u0169ng theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Telegraph, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man xanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua Per Mertesacker l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Laurent Koscielny \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/4-van-de-hlv-emery-can-giai-quyet-truoc-mua-giai-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Unai Emery n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Mertesacker \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Arsenal c\u00f2n Koscielny ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 10 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, HLV Emery \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKoscielny, Petr Cech, Aaron Ramsey, Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2241","checkdouble":"194239"},{"date":"10:19 11/08","title":"HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thibaut Courtois d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Petr Cech ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Thibaut Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Courtois l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu thi \u0111\u1ea5u, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1ea7n g\u0169i c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Courtois \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, The Blues thu v\u1ec1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Bernabeu kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n. L\u00fd do l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Los Blancos l\u00e0 v\u00ec gia \u0111\u00ecnh, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf g\u1ea7n c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1ee7a Courtois?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Thibaut Courtois, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge t\u1edbi Bernabeu c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri\" title=\"Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 l\u1eafm. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi Real Madrid. D\u00f9 sao c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, t\u00f4i ch\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Eden Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y 3 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 l\u1ea7n, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Stamford Bridge v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi Kepa c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Courtois hay kh\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Kepa s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng do Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Mateo Kovacic \u00f4ng chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1edbi Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2240","checkdouble":"194240"},{"date":"09:13 11/08","title":"Klopp v\u1eabn cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ramos l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/klopp-van-cay-cu-va-khang-dinh-ramos-la-noi-si-nhuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fenerbahce h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-194142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, song c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Fenerbahce-muon-dua-Divock-Origi-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Divock Origi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Origi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Watford, Crystal Palace hay Wolves, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Origi t\u1edbi Fenerbahce l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n HLV Klopp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Origi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Origi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Origi\" title=\"Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/29/sao-xit-liverpool-doi-lenh-klopp-de-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Origi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTTCN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2239","checkdouble":"194241"},{"date":"09:12 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-stoke-vs-brentford-21h00-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Stoke vs Brentford l\u00fac 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Stoke vs Brentford 21h ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Stoke-vs-Brentford.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Stoke vs Brentford</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Stoke vs Brentford: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Stoke \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i, khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365 c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t nh\u01b0 Shaqiri, Ramadan Sobhi, Marc Muniesa hay Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i HLV Gary Rowett c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 Oghenekaro Etebo, Adam Federici, James McClean, Tom Ince hay Sam Clucas.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00f9a H\u00e8, Stoke r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 6 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi Walsall. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tan n\u00e1t 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Leeds United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 2, Stoke c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u tay, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brendford, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. \u1ede 2 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u00f3, Stoke \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1eeda tr\u00ean b\u1edfi l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBrenford \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e2n binh Rotherham United, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u xa nh\u00e0.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2238","checkdouble":"194242"},{"date":"11:01 11/08","title":"HLV Emery khi\u1ebfn NHM Arsenal bu\u1ed3n vui l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-emery-khien-nhm-arsenal-buon-vui-lan-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb Ramsey song kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Arsenal s\u1eafp gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Ramsey</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Aaron Ramsey\" title=\"Aaron Ramsey\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ramsey</span>, Real v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e1o tin vui t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Arsenal<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Ramsey, HLV Unai Emery c\u00f2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ospina bat chinh truoc Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Ospina b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Unai-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ospina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Carl Jenkinson, David Ospina v\u00e0 Joel Campbell c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n hay b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a BL\u0110&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Emile Smith Rowe v\u00e0 Eddie Nketiah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2237","checkdouble":"194244"},{"date":"11:08 11/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/7/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fenerbahce h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n Origi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-southampton-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tien-dao-cua-liverpool-172-194142.html\" target=\"_blank\">Danny Ings t\u1edbi Southampton</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, song c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Divock Origi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/26/Fenerbahce-muon-dua-Divock-Origi-roi-Liverpool-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Divock Origi mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Firmino, Sturridge v\u00e0 Solanke, b\u1edfi v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Origi, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Watford, Crystal Palace hay Wolves, song s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Liverpool y\u00eau c\u1ea7u khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 26 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Origi t\u1edbi Fenerbahce l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n HLV Klopp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Origi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Fenerbahce c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Liverpool v\u00e0 Origi \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Origi\" title=\"Origi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/29/sao-xit-liverpool-doi-lenh-klopp-de-ra-di.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Origi s\u1eafp t\u1edbi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Origi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00ec The Kop c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTTCN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Origi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2236","checkdouble":"194245"},{"date":"11:22 11/08","title":"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Arsenal, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eafp c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dembele</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcom, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ousmane Dembele b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/khong-phai-arsenal-day-moi-la-doi-bong-sap-co-dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ousmane Dembele t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chia tay Barca \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/dembele-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-arsenal-184-194031.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele</span>, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a c\u00f3 k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ebfn Arsenal, phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ef1u sao Dortmund.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh Ousmane Dembele</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n mua Ousmane Dembele c\u1ee7a Barca, theo Mundo Deportivo \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 120 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ousmane Dembele co the roi Camp Nou neu Barca mua Willian\" title=\"Ousmane Dembele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Camp Nou n\u1ebfu Barca mua Willian\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/arsenal-tung-chieu-doc-so-huu-dembele-khien-barca-nga-ngua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ousmane Dembele\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p lo ng\u1ea1i Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe s\u1ebd ra \u0111i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel tin r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng PSG, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed s\u1ebd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1997. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Dembele \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, b\u1edfi v\u1eady anh \u01b0u ti\u00ean \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn PSG \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho b\u1ed9 ba Mbappe, Cavani v\u00e0 Neymar. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2235","checkdouble":"194246"},{"date":"10:38 11/08","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-mu-21-leicester.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M.U \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 \u00fd, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. \r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paul Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPaul Pogba m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng M.U, song anh \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng. S\u1ed1 6 \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m khi\u1ebfn Kasper Schmeichel ph\u1ea3i b\u00f3 tay. Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong 11 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, san b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Ryan Babel.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a M.U, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec1u qua ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Pogba, anh chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: HLV Claude Puel</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, HLV Claude Puel t\u1ef1 tin tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1: &ldquo;Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, song Leicester \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Claude Puel phat bieu ve tran MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Claude Puel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/hlv-claude-puel-giai-thich-ly-do-tai-sao-leicester-that-bai-truoc-mu.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Claude Puel kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t h\u00f9ng h\u1ed3n, song Leicester c\u1ee7a Claude Puel ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Old Trafford, ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vardy ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLeicester ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua (3 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 5 thua). \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 8 trong 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gh\u00e9 th\u0103m s\u00e2n Old Trafford (h\u00f2a 1).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Luke Shaw</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 Ashley Young v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau World Cup 2018, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Luke Shaw ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester </span>v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" title=\"Luke Shaw ghi ban dau tien cho M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luke Shaw c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. C\u1ef1u sao Southampton l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (99) v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t (67) b\u00ean ph\u00eda Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuke Shaw c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, anh khi\u1ebfn Ricardo Pereira b\u00ean ph\u00eda Leicester kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, Shaw c\u00f2n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho M.U sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 67 cho h\u1ecd tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, Shaw x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Wes Morgan</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Wes Morgan \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao 34 tu\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c khi\u1ebfn Morgan kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wes Morgan co mot tran dau that vong\" title=\"Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/morgan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wes Morgan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1984 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, anh t\u1ecf ra ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Morgan \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb Sanchez lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe s\u1eafc l\u1eb9m, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Harry Maguire.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Morgan \u1edf Old Trafford l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMorgan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Leicester trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi M.U, n\u1ebfu c\u1ee9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Jonny Evans.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Jose Mourinho</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U, \u00f4ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BL\u0110 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1. Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester khi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n&nbsp;th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" title=\"Mourinho tran M.U vs Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/danh-bai-leicester-mourinho-ca-ngoi-suc-manh-tap-the-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u00f9ng MU c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ee7a v\u00e2y, song Mourinho v\u1eabn gi\u00fap M.U c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester gi\u00fap Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Old Trafford v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 55 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp trung trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Jose Mourinho b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u1ea3 18 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV (th\u1eafng 11, h\u00f2a 7), ri\u00eang t\u1ea1i Premier League, &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; th\u1eafng 9 trong s\u1ed1 10 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n (h\u00f2a 1).&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean d\u1eb7n d\u00f2 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i, ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c M.U ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Alexis Sanchez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alexis Sanchez l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 cho M.U qu\u1ea3 11m ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 Paul Pogba th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sanchez de mat bong qua nhieu truoc Leicester\" title=\"Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/sanchez.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sanchez \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t sung s\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Sanchez kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, Sanchez g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung v\u1edbi Rashford v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Sanchez c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 23 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng, nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. Mourinho ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Sanchez ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn NHM Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: David de Gea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David de Gea v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea MU\" title=\"De Gea MU\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/de-gea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Gea ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester, De Gea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ph\u00fat 28, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ef1c nhanh sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Maddison, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 75 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 De Gea ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Gray.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, trong hi\u1ec7p 1 De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ee9u thua nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n anh l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong 90 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2234","checkdouble":"194247"},{"date":"11:42 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nantes vs Monaco 22h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-nantes-vs-monaco-22h00-ngay-118-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nantes vs Monaco l\u00fac 22h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nantes vs Monaco 22h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nantes vs Monaco 22h00 ng\u00e0y 118 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nantes-vs-Monaco.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nantes vs Monaco</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Nantes vs Monaco: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Nantes k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9 Ligue 1 v\u00e0 n\u0103m nay m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf n\u1eeda tr\u00ean BXH. Trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Nantes kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1. C\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n De la Beaujoire, ngo\u00e0i ra th\u00ec Nantes c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fabio v\u00e0 Lucas Evangelista c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Boschilia \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh Monaco .<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda CLB x\u1ee9 C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn khi Lemar, Moutinho, Fabinho, Meite hay Diakhaby \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Monaco ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Pierre-Gabriel, Aholou v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Golovin \u2013 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua. Tuy v\u1eady, Golovin v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n suy y\u1ebfu kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng Monaco v\u1eabn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 6 l\u1ea7n l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nantes, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 Monaco d\u00f9 m\u1ea1nh hay y\u1ebfu. V\u1eady n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y!<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nantes \u0111\u1ec1u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi rung. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed1c d\u01b0\u1edbi cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\nNantes th\u1eafng 1 v\u00e0 thua 8 trong 10 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9. Nantes c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 thua 3 trong 5 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Monaco m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nNantes: Pallois v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t v\u00ec l\u00fd do c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\nMonaco: Golovin ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Almamy Toure b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong khi Sidibe v\u00e0 Subasic v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2233","checkdouble":"194248"},{"date":"11:54 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lille vs Rennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-lille-vs-rennes-01h00-ngay-128-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lille vs Rennes l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 12/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lille vs Rennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Lille vs Rennes 01h00 ng\u00e0y 128 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Lille-vs-Rennes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lille vs Rennes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>Lille vs Rennes: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Lille ph\u1ec9a chia tay Yves Bissouma, Ibrahim Amadou v\u00e0 K\u00e9vin Malcuit th\u00ec Rennes c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m Joris Gnagnon.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Lille \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp c\u1eeda tr\u00ean nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao, d\u1eabu v\u1eady, v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Lille. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Lille \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi ch\u01a1i 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 4 th\u1eafng, 2 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua 1. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Rennes \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t b\u1eb1ng khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 sau 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u01a1n n\u1eefa, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Lille \u1eaft h\u1eb3n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u00fa h\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nhau 37 l\u1ea7n, Lille th\u1eafng 14, h\u00f2a 15 v\u00e0 thua 9 tr\u1eadn.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2232","checkdouble":"194249"},{"date":"08:02 11/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (11/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1182018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='styleshe