n-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t v\u1edbi HLV Mourinho, Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111eo tr\u00ean tay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo;</h2>\r\nPaul Pogba l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3. N\u00e0o l\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 4 ng\u00e0y sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8, n\u00e0o l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u \u0111i v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u00ea. Nh\u01b0 HLV Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i kho\u1ea3ng 60 ph\u00fat. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t 84 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba tr\u1eadn MU 2-1 Leicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Paul-Pogba-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester-da-toa-sang-ruc-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Valencia, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U trong ng\u00e0y m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19. Ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Mourinho. Th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 qu\u00ean \u0111i s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o t\u1eeb Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd Pogba l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i hay \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. N\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn, Mourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i g\u1ecdi Pogba l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;. Anh di chuy\u1ec3n kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ea3 trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Ch\u00ednh Pogba l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng qu\u1ea3 penalty ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3, m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU 2-1 Leicester B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU 2-1 Leicester B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/MU-2-1-Leicester-Bong-dang-Sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u1eadn M.U 2-1 Leicester l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ch\u00ea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez, b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi Wes Morgan song v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eadp tr\u00fang tay c\u1ee7a Daniel Amartey. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Andre Marriner ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n. Sau m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tranh lu\u1eadn n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u1edbi Sanchez, Pogba l\u0129nh tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 11m. Anh thong dong, \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u01b0a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn Pogba ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Anh t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i M.U c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Leicester c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t&rdquo; ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-gay-soc-pogba-la-mot-con-quai-thu-172-194225.html\">Mourinho g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: &ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i th\u00fa&rdquo;</span><br>\r\n<span>Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y. HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMay m\u00e0 c\u00f3 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3, M.U ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 cho Leicester l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn hi\u1ec7p 1. Nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft B\u1ea7y c\u00e1o l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a David de Gea, l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a James Maddison.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Mourinho \u1edf b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 v\u1ebb lo l\u1eafng khi M.U b\u1ecb Leicester l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt. \u00d4ng c\u00e0ng b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i h\u01a1n khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Romelu Lukaku khi \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Schmeichel d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Pogba\" title=\"Mourinho va Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Mourinho-va-Pogba.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t Pogba</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eadt may l\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Pogba, M.U \u0111\u00e3 v\u1edbt v\u00e1t l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. H\u1ecd ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 6 \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 83, Luke Shaw kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Juan Mata n\u00e2ng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00ean 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ra ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hoan ngh\u00eanh nhi\u1ec7t li\u1ec7t t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Mourinho d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i v\u1ed7 vai nh\u1eb9 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda sau nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng khai r\u1eb1ng gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 r\u1ea1n n\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" title=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Pogba-toa-sang-giup-M.U-ha-Leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Jamie Vardy kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Leicester tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-1. M.U kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 bao, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 Pogba hay Alexis Sanchez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng M.U, Pogba ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t &ldquo;Si\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo; xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau MU 2-1 Leicester\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Thong-tin-sau-tran-MU-2-1-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u MU 2-1 Leicester</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u M.U 2-1 Leicester (V\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_278846\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/08/11/manutd-leicester-1533934869.mp4&amp;autoplay=true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2230","checkdouble":"194228"},{"date":"08:13 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Aston Villa vs Wigan 21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-aston-villa-vs-wigan-21h00-ngay-118-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Derby County vs Leeds l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Leeds 23h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Derby-County-vs-Leeds.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Derby County vs Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span>Derby County vs Leeds: 2-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Trong kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc cho Derby County trong nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leeds. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2005, Derby County th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn 9/12 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leeds tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pride Park (thua 1). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Derby County t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n HLV Frank Lampard to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ghi 13 b\u00e0n. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Derby County \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Reading v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf l\u1ea1i Pride Park c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lampard. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leeds Utd v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. D\u01b0\u1edbi quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV c\u00e1o gi\u00e0 Marcelo Bielsa, The Whites v\u1eeba c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec1-pa cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u201cng\u1ecdt\u201d h\u01a1n, khi h\u1ea1 knock-out Stoke City (\u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng t\u1eeb Premier League) 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 TLCA, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y (th\u1eafng 2). Th\u1ebf n\u00ean, l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn phe kh\u00e1ch.\u00a0 <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 83 tr\u1eadn, Derby County th\u1eafng 33, h\u00f2a 16, thua 34.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derby County, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 22, h\u00f2a 9, thua 11. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nDerby County: Chris Martin (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng); Ikechi Anya (kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn).\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 <br>\r\nLeeds Utd: \u0110\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2229","checkdouble":"194229"},{"date":"08:16 11/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea (21h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): Nh\u1ea3y m\u00faa c\u00f9ng Sarriball","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/nhan-dinh-huddersfield-vs-chelsea-21h00-ngay-118-nhay-mua-cung-sarriball.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean Sarri. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2017/18.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nChelsea trong l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thua 0-2 t\u1ea1i si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Man City &ldquo;v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i&rdquo; k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Sau tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf l\u1ea1i n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi m\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian sa th\u1ea3i Conte, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mua \u0111\u1eaft b\u00e1n r\u1ebb, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Chelsea \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi thu n\u1ea1p th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 Kepa v\u00e0 Kovacic, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi tri\u1ec3n &ldquo;Sarriball&rdquo; &ndash; chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda m\u00e0 Napoli t\u1eebng tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Nhan-dinh-Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-vong-1-Premier-League-201819-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169, l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1. Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau nh\u01b0 Man City c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, l\u00e0m quen l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadt may cho Sarri, khi \u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Thibaut Courtois, v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Eden Hazard. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung t\u00e2n binh Jorginho &ndash; c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 Chelsea h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t may cho Sarri, khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng Huddersfield, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong c\u00e1ch m\u1edbi &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec The Blues \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nHuddersfield kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a David Wagner \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &ldquo;to\u00e0n m\u1ea1ng&rdquo;. Huddersfield \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, giai \u0111o\u1ea1n 2 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Kirklees.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd thua t\u1edbi 10 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m d\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ecbch 2018, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap The Terriers tr\u1ee5 l\u1ea1i \u1edf Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Huddersfield v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Preview Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1182018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Huddersfield v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV David Wagner c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Chelsea v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a The Blues, m\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft, Huddersfield &ldquo;s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c duy nh\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Chelsea c\u0169ng thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Burnley &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o h\u00e0ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Huddersfield vs Chelsea v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Chelsea vs Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/chelsea1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea th\u1eafng Huddersfield 3-1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Chelsea 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Hudderfield th\u1eafng Chelsea tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 64 n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n trong 5/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a 2, thua 2 trong 7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Huddersfield thua 10 tr\u1eadn, ki\u1ebfm v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 &ndash; \u00edt h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 5 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8, nh\u01b0ng 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t g\u1eb7p Huddersfield \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc (3-1, 1-1)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- Chelsea ch\u1ec9 thua 1 trong 19 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n \u1edf Premier League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kovacic v\u00e0 Kepa trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Courtois, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Caballero s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 theo phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Sarri, v\u1edbi Luiz &ndash; Rudier l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Hazard v\u00e0 Willian b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huddersfield kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Danny Williams, Erik D\u1ee7m v\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh Juninho Bacuna.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Huddersfield-vs-Chelsea-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-3-3).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Huddersfield vs Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1&nbsp;Huddersfield vs Chelsea: 1-2</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-truoc-mua-giai-201819-tan-cong-va-hon-the-nua-172-193858.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: T\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa</span><br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Top 4, HLV Sarri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0a The Blues tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-chelsea-len-tieng-xac-nhan-tuong-lai-cua-hazard-172-194216.html\">HLV Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Hazard</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, d\u1eadp t\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2228","checkdouble":"194230"},{"date":"08:37 11/08","title":"Pogba n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-leicester-tran-dau-vong-1-premier-league-201819-372-194203.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU vs Leicester</span> trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Paul-Pogba-phat-bieu-ve-MU-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Leicester-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u201cB\u1ea7y c\u00e1o\u201d, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 91 l\u1ea7n, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 68 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 54 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9, 6 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, 2 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, 2 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Pogba, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester nh\u01b0ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" title=\"Pogba toa sang giup M.U ha Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/pogba-noi-gi-sau-khi-toa-sang-truoc-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o sau World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n trong th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay ngay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Mourinho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, l\u00fac n\u00e0y t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n cho CLB, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng M.U chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2227","checkdouble":"194231"}]}